cff-version: 1.2.0
message: 'If you reference this library, please cite it as below.'
title: 'lattice — reference library of complex systems models'
abstract: >-
  A reference library of validated complex systems models. Each model page
  presents an interactive simulation, the underlying math, a plain-language
  explanation, and citations back to the source literature. Browser engines
  are mirrored by Python reference implementations and validated against the
  closed-form analytic results, where they exist.
authors:
